
Description:

  Stops GUI mode and places the tool into Tcl mode, running in the Vivado
  Design Suite Tcl shell. In Tcl mode, all commands must be entered as Tcl
  commands or through Tcl scripts.

Arguments:

  -verbose - (Optional) Temporarily override any message limits and return
  all messages from this command.

  Note: Message limits can be defined with the set_msg_config command.

Examples:

  The following example stops and closes the GUI and places the tool into Tcl
  mode:

    stop_gui

See Also:

   *  start_gui
